metadata.name: INNERSPACE #1
metadata.description:
The past two years felt like an incredible journey.
The highs, the lows, the beautiful people I've met along the ride.
And the desire to make music regardless of everything else.

To put all my FAITH in camoufly was the right decision, I believe.
But before camoufly even started I was already trying to improve my craft, expressing myself through music.
I was trying to find my SOUND, while trying to find myself.

"INNERSPACE" embodies the depths of this research.
And it's one of the first songs that came along during my everlong journey through sounds, melting together inspirations and expeirments.

This is to every single person that came across my music.
Thank you for being here on this journey with me.
This is "INNERSPACE".
